            "cons_heading_override": "✕ What Held It Back",
            "bottom_line": "<p>Great for grip strength and wrist rehab. Not great for the \"slim, toned arms\" goal most women are actually after. If you're an athlete or recovering from an injury, worth looking at. Otherwise, the 360° Trainer does more for less money.</p>",
