            "cons_heading_override": "✕ What Held It Back",
            "bottom_line": "<p>The cheapest option, and it shows — not in quality, but in the psychology of use. If you have the self-discipline to follow a structured program consistently, bands will work. Most people don't, and that's fine. That's why the 360° Trainer exists.</p>",
