            "visual_title": "Arm Trimmer Sleeves",
            "visual_note": "Heat Compression · \"3x More Sweat\"",
            "grade": "C+",
            "tone": "neutral",
            "specs": "",
            "summary": "<p>I feel the need to be direct here because these are everywhere on social media right now, and they're being sold with some very misleading claims. Arm trimmer sleeves generate heat and increase sweat around your arms. That's real. What's not real is the implication that sweating more means losing arm fat.</p><p>The water weight you lose through sweat comes back the moment you drink water. If you're doing actual exercise while wearing them, the exercise is doing the work — not the sleeves. Several women in my test group purchased these before joining the study. Not a single one saw arm circumference reduction from the sleeves alone.</p>",
            "how_steps": "",
            "metrics": "",
            "testimonials": "",
            "pros": "",
            "cons": "",
            "bottom_line": "<p>They feel like they're working because you're hot and sweaty. They aren't actually doing the work. Save your money — or spend it on something that does.</p>",
